cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper proposes a method for open-set recognition in image classification datasets using class conditioned auto-encoders. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves training and testing methodology, which suggests it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves statistical modeling, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, since the experiments are performed on image classification datasets, it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
